Description:
    This will generate the necessary files for super simple authentication. 

    Your password is located in config/super_simple_authentication.yml

Example:
    ./script/generate super_simple_authentication sessions

    This will create:
        app/controllers/sessions_controller.rb
        app/views/sessions/new.rhtml
        config/super_simple_authentication.yml
        lib/super_simple_authentication_system.yml